Mavin Gaye is about to have a biopic, Variety Reports. Dr. Dre is fortunate to receive an approval from Gaye’s family. Over the years, the likes of Cameron Crowe, Jamie Foxx, and Jesse L. Martin have tried to get the same approval.  That is not all. Dr. Dre has secured the rights to the icon’s music. However, Dr. Dre is in a mix. His lawyers are the King, Holmes, Paterno and Soriano, the same firm that represented Pharrell.